# Desktop switching using Function keys
Key F1	A $[Mod1]	GotoPage 0 0
Key F2  A $[Mod1]	GotoPage 1 0
Key F3  A $[Mod1]	GotoPage 2 0
Key F4  A $[Mod1]	GotoPage 3 0
Key F5  A $[Mod1]	GotoPage 4 0
Key F6  A $[Mod1]	GotoPage 5 0
Key F7  A $[Mod1]	GotoPage 6 0
Key F8  A $[Mod1]	GotoPage 7 0
Key F9	A $[Mod1]	GotoPage 8 0
Key F10	A $[Mod1]	GotoPage 9 0
Key F11	A $[Mod1]	GotoPage 10 0
Key F12	A $[Mod1]	GotoPage 11 0

# Go to previouse page using Escape
Key Escape A $[Mod1]	GotoPage prev

# Move focused window to the selected desktop page
Key F1  A $[Mod2]	MoveToPage-Focus 0 0
Key F2  A $[Mod2]	MoveToPage-Focus 1 0
Key F3  A $[Mod2]	MoveToPage-Focus 2 0
Key F4  A $[Mod2]	MoveToPage-Focus 3 0
Key F5  A $[Mod2]	MoveToPage-Focus 4 0
Key F6  A $[Mod2]	MoveToPage-Focus 5 0
Key F7  A $[Mod2]	MoveToPage-Focus 6 0
Key F8  A $[Mod2]	MoveToPage-Focus 7 0
Key F9	A $[Mod2]	MoveToPage-Focus 8 0
Key F10	A $[Mod2]	MoveToPage-Focus 9 0
Key F11	A $[Mod2]	MoveToPage-Focus 10 0
Key F12	A $[Mod2]	MoveToPage-Focus 11 0

# Move focused window to the last used page
Key Escape A $[Mod2]	MoveToPage-Focus prev

# vim:ft=fvwm
